text: Kutlubulatovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Abitovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 219 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Meleuz, 3 km from Basurmanovka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Kutlubulatovo
